title: The Year in Special Operations 2014-2015
description:
The Year in Special Operations 2014-2015

Now in its ninth year in print, The Year in Special Operations details the major initiatives being undertaken in the upcoming 12 months. The publication is produced with the input and assistance of each of the special warfare units within the Department of Defense. This high-quality, perfect-bound publication is a salute to these elite soldiers, sailors, airmen, and Marines, as well as an in-depth analysis and forecast of the current global conditions and scenarios in which they operate
